content.html: I'm gonna tell late night twitter two secrets: 1) Good speakers practice a lot. A lot. Sitting, standing, with their remote. Without their remote. With a timer. A lot. 2) I don't know a single tech conference speaker who doesn't get nervous.

I'm gonna tell late night twitter two secrets:

1) Good speakers practice a lot. A lot. Sitting, standing, with their remote. Without their remote. With a timer. A lot. 

2) I don't know a single tech conference speaker who doesn't get nervous.
